metadata.name: Death
metadata.description:
[ The cold grasp your hands,
mist gently embrace your soul.
Content fills your heart. ]

The end of the road leads us to Atropos' embrace. Though her eyes are always covered, she is all-seeing.

The lullaby from childhood is gone, and the festive music of life, muted. Nothing but silence is in the air as Atropos sways with what remains of human life.
